		Crystalize ... Freeze/Static/Auto-grab some parameters
		Forker ....... Using generic semanthics decide operations
		Parser ....... Dispacher
		Processor .... Argumented/verbs for operations (aaa ...)
		Shadow ....... Pre-process/Control-access before the real command
		+
		Private ...... me-* prefix
	
	Cases
		Raw .......... Standard script for computing/automation
		Explicitor ... Show Help & Code snippets ready to argument
		Security ..... Extra check or warn the user...
		Leverage ..... Generic semanthics to override actions by argument
		Overloads .... pre-processing of arguments/results
		Decorators ... pre/post work of standard scripts
		Reiterate .... Inform about the alternative command
		Tooling ...... Tools to manage this ecosystem (like code/X/XX)

